---

<BaseLayout
  title="3-Day Safari: Tarangire & Ngorongoro | Go Kilimanjaro Treks"
  description="Three-day Tanzania safari covering Tarangire National Park and Ngorongoro Crater."
  schemas={schemas}
>
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="page-hero-eyebrow">Tanzania Safari Itinerary</span>
    <h1>3-Day Safari: Tarangire &amp; Ngorongoro.</h1>
    <p>Three-day Tanzania safari covering Tarangire National Park and Ngorongoro Crater.</p>
    <div class="hero-ctas">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Request a Quote &#x2192;</a>
      <a href="https://wa.me/255677917500" class="btn-ghost" target="_blank" rel="noopener">&#x1F4AC; WhatsApp Nelson</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section-white">
  <div class="container" style="max-width:820px">
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">3: DAYS SAFARI - TARANGIRE &amp; NGORONGORO CRATER</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Experience two of Northern Tanzania's most iconic wildlife destinations on this exciting short safari. From the giant elephant herds and ancient baobab trees of Tarangire National Park to the breathtaking wildlife-rich Ngorongoro Crater, this itinerary offers an unforgettable African safari experience.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Price start From 750 USD.</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Day 1: Tarangire National Park</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Depart from Arusha and drive to Tarangire National Park for a full-day game drive. Famous for its large elephant population, majestic baobab trees, and diverse landscapes, Tarangire provides excellent wildlife viewing opportunities throughout the year.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">During your safari, you may encounter elephants, lions, giraffes, zebras, wildebeests, buffaloes, impalas, warthogs, and a variety of bird species. The Tarangire River attracts abundant wildlife, making it one of the best game-viewing areas in Northern Tanzania.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Enjoy a picnic lunch inside the park before continuing with an afternoon game drive.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Later, drive to Karatu for dinner and overnight at Accomodation : Bougainvillea Safari Lodge.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Meal Plan: Lunch &amp; Dinner</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Day 2: Ngorongoro Crater - Return to Arusha</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">After breakfast, drive to the spectacular  and descend into the crater for a full-day game drive.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Known as one of Africa's natural wonders, the crater hosts an extraordinary concentration of wildlife including lions, elephants, buffaloes, zebras, wildebeests, hippos, hyenas, and the endangered black rhino. The crater floor's unique ecosystem provides excellent opportunities to observe wildlife in a stunning setting.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Enjoy a picnic lunch at a designated picnic site within the crater before continuing your game drive.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">In the afternoon, ascend the crater and drive back to Arusha for overnight.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Accommodation : Forest Hill Hotel.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Meal Plan: DBBL</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Day 4: Departure</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">After breakfast, transfer to the airport for your onward flight, marking the end of your memorable Tanzania safari adventure.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Meal Plan: Breakfast</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Price Included</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">• Park entrance fees and conservation fees</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">• Ngorongoro Crater service fee</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">• Professional English-speaking safari guide</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">• Private 4x4 safari vehicle with pop-up roof</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">• 1 night's accommodation</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">• Meals as specified in the itinerary</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">• Bottled drinking water during safari</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">• Government taxes and VAT</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Not Included</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">• International and domestic flights</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">• Travel insurance</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">• Visa fees</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">• Alcoholic and soft drinks</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">• Tips and gratuities</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">• Personal expenses and items of a personal nature</p>
  </div>
</section>

